PYI032 [*] Prefer `object` to `Any` for the second parameter to `__eq__`
 --> PYI032.pyi:6:29
  |
5 | class Bad:
6 |     def __eq__(self, other: Any) -> bool: ...  # PYI032
  |                             ^^^
7 |     def __ne__(self, other: typing.Any) -> typing.Any: ...  # PYI032
  |
help: Replace with `object`
  |
